@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Manage Availability

' =========================================================
' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps map to actions)
' Step 1  Host opens availability for a listing.
' Step 2  Host selects action (block dates or open dates).
' Step 3  Host selects date range.
' Step 4  System validates range.
' Step 5  If invalid, system shows error (end).
' Step 6  If valid, system updates availability slots.
' Step 7  System shows updated calendar (end).
' =========================================================

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam DefaultFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 14
skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 30

|Host|
start
:1. Open availability;
:2. Choose block/open;
:3. Select date range;

|System|
:4. Validate date range;

if (Valid?) then (Yes)
  :6. Update availability slots;
  :7. Show updated calendar;
  stop
else (No)
  :5. Show error;
  stop
endif

@enduml